## Data Types 



#### Non-Explicit

```kotlin
// Data Types

//    Integer
    val wholeNumber = 3
//    Long Integer
    val bigNumber = 3L
//    Float
    val preciseDecimal = 3.3
//    D
    val decimal = 3.3f
//    Booleans
    val isVegetal = false
    val isMeat = true
//    Char
    val justaChar = 'a'
```


